'''Hutt! Hutt! Hutt!''' (A Bonus Expanded Universe Feature on Notorious Hutts of the Star Wars Universe) is a series of [[Roleplaying game|RPG]] scenarios written by [[Cory J. Herndon]] released on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] web site from [[September 11]] to [[December 4]], [[2003]].

